data.description: ****MULTIPLE OFFERS HAVE BEEN RECEIVED. SELLERS ARE REQUESTING BEST AND FINAL BIDS BY MONDAY AT 5 PM.  Opportunity awaits!   Don’t miss out on this 1,400 sf townhouse offering a comfortable and spacious living experience with 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths. As you step inside, you are greeted by a welcoming living room featuring a large picture window that flows to the adjacent dining room, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests. The dining room opens up to a generously sized eat-in kitchen with ample cabinetry and counter space, providing room for culinary creativity. Connected to the kitchen is a cozy den with a sliding door that leads to a small fenced-in yard, offering a private outdoor retreat. Convenience is key with a half bath and laundry room situated on main floor. The townhome also features a one-car attached garage for secure parking and additional storage. Upstairs, you'll find 3 bedrooms two of which are spacious and 2 full baths, providing comfort and privacy for all occupants. This property boasts good natural light throughout, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. After making some needed updates, you can transform this house into a wonderful home that suits your lifestyle.  Being sold strictly as-is. Fantastic location!  Highly respected school system, walking distance to the elementary school and close to major highways and shopping galore!
